## D-009 — Free tier boundary

**Date:** 2026-04-22
**Status:** Active

**First 5 providers free for 12 months.** Slot allocation at Platform Admin discretion, recorded in the tenant/provider contract row.

After the 12-month free period: provider transitions to **per-seat / package SaaS subscription** (pricing TBD by founder pre-Sprint 15) **plus** the 25% commission per `D-007`. Subscription does **not** displace commission.

Rationale: loss leader to seed the platform with a credible provider mix across categories; subscription introduces predictable MRR; commission keeps incentives aligned with bringing real value (LVJ-originated revenue).

Tracking: `Tenant.freeTierExpiresAt` + `ServiceProvider.freeTierExpiresAt` columns. Cron in Sprint 15 sweeps expiring tiers and triggers the subscription onboarding flow 30 days prior.

