## D-010 — Marketing-HITL SLA: 24h

**Date:** 2026-04-22
**Status:** Active

All marketing content (blog drafts, social posts, public Service Provider Directory listings, AI-generated visa-explainer updates) requires marketing-HITL approval within **24 hours** of being placed in the queue at `/admin/marketing-approvals`.

Rationale: marketing has a different cadence than legal (slower, less time-critical, but volume is higher). 24h matches industry norms for content review while keeping the publishing pipeline fast enough to ship.

Implementation: `HITLApproval.tier = 'MARKETING'`; SLA breach surfaces on Platform Marketing dashboard.

