## D-012 — LLM cost caps

**Date:** 2026-04-22
**Status:** Active

|Scope             |Soft cap (warn + pause non-critical)|Hard cap (pause all)|
|------------------|------------------------------------|--------------------|
|Per tenant        |$50/day                             |$100/day            |
|Platform marketing|$30/day                             |$75/day             |
|Platform-wide     |—                                   |**$200/day**        |

Reset: UTC midnight. Override: Platform Admin only, audit-logged with reason.

Rationale: per-tenant cap protects tenants from runaway agent loops on their data; platform marketing cap is owned by LVJ growth budget and isolated from tenant budgets; platform-wide hard cap catches systemic failures (e.g., infinite loop across many tenants).

Implementation: `services/cost-guard.ts` reads `AutomationLog.costUsd` rolling 24h sum per scope; emits `cost.threshold.warn` and `cost.threshold.pause` events.

