## D-016 — Stripe Connect from day 1

**Date:** 2026-04-22
**Status:** Active

Provider payouts use Stripe Connect from launch, not manual invoice/wire-transfer for the first cohort.

Rationale: manual settlement is operationally painful even at low volume; Stripe Connect onboarding is well-understood; doing it later means re-doing every provider’s onboarding.

Implementation: Sprint 8.5 (self-serve onboarding) includes Stripe Connect Express onboarding for providers; Sprint 15 ships the monthly settlement cron.

